    {
      "id": "1b14750c-f3ba-801c-b59a-c5ef40dbd3b4",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Authors propose a recourse framework aimed at providers of content. Essencially, the recommender has a set of rules that, if fulfilled, lead to a change in ranking or recommendation. Validation of this dataset on 3 public datasets shows RecRec is effective at leading to valid, sparse and actionable recommendations.",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
